{"tid":2064052,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[改詞] 飛花仲夏（原：櫻花樹下 - 張敬軒）","createTime":"2020-06-14T13:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T07:36:00.000Z","uid":257847,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c5a51a40e9529d128285543902cd9fcd4a1eee31","tid":2064052,"uid":257847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T13:45:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">飛花仲夏</span><br />\n原曲：櫻花樹下<br />\n原詞：林若寧   <br />\n作曲：伍卓賢<br />\n編曲：劉志遠<br />\n<br />\n靜看那位少年 某日要搬遷<br />\n悲泣過枕邊進眠 期望降落遠方伊甸<br />\n共你縱不相見 至少可並肩<br />\n琴樂奏起心中扣弦 鳴笛炮火槍聲響遍<br />\n我倆手牽<br />\n<br />\n曾赤手抵擋困境 同伴堅守這絕嶺<br />\n當天圍城 多得你和應 故事傳詠<br />\n誰隻身今天遠征 遺憾不親眼做證<br />\n誰倒影 誰死拚 紀念 刻銘 萬個大名<br />\n來日相約定傾聽<br />\n<br />\n異國那位少年 日報看一篇<br />\n家鄉正急速改變 無力痛苦至想抽煙<br />\n共你再不相見 哪位可代主演<br />\n懷念戰火高呼向前 迎著炮彈都不抖顫<br />\n縱有硝煙<br />\n<br />\n曾赤手抵擋困境 同伴堅守這絕嶺<br />\n當天圍城 多得你和應 戰事未停<br />\n誰隻身今天遠征 遺憾不親眼做證<br />\n誰倒影 誰死拚 堅定 率領 萬眾取勝<br />\n聽我鏗鏘歌聲<br />\n<br />\n也許心灰痛楚 都不折挫 <br />\n上鎖 也阻不到我 決意高歌<br />\n哪畏懼面前烈火 通通都走過<br />\n<br />\n如有天張開眼睛 能共手跟你做證<br />\n當天餘情 當天那份勁 繼續高擎<br />\n如某天注定逃命 仍在等跟你共取勝<br />\n一併 堅挺 肩並 心永未結冰<br />\n明日請 創造遠景<br />\n<br />\n==========================================<br />\n以下係小弟之前改既一啲拙作<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家多多支持<br />\n<br />\n[改詞] 約誓 （原：償還 - 王菲）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fyyyPS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fyyyPS</a><br />\n<br />\n[改詞] 支國失調（原：思覺失調 - 劉浩龍）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fzhfHS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fzhfHS</a><br />\n<br />\n[改詞] 粵語長片（原：粵語殘片 - 陳奕迅）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2056180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2056180</a><br />\n<br />\n[改詞] 幫吳重儀改咗段詞（原：月球上的人 節錄 - 陳奕迅）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2061525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2061525</a>"},{"pid":"d7398b1a4dd9586d9572547ce47f25cc6de0f39a","tid":2064052,"uid":257847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T13:46:04.000Z","msg":"呻下：<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日晏晝收到一位好朋友既訊息，話佢因為安全問題而要暫時離開呢場抗爭<br />\n收到消息之後我有啲傷心，所以改咗呢份詞去抒發一下<br />\n由於時間較為倉猝，所以都改得麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好忘記因為呢場運動受迫害而要離開香港、甚至係一啲已經離開咗我哋既朋友。<br />\n喺海外既巴絲，希望你哋都安好，我將會喺度等待你哋返嚟既一日。 <br />\n<br />\n聽日 (6月15日) 就係梁凌杰先生離開我哋既一週年，第一位因為呢場運動犧牲既朋友。唔知大家仲記唔記得當日自己既心情係點，我自己喊咗成晚。<br />\n但係梁先生用自己既生命喚醒咗部分人，希望大家唔好忘記佢、亦唔好忘記所有被政權迫害而離世既人，即使你唔知道佢哋既姓名。<br />\n但願大家可以記得佢哋，唔好因為時間而忘記、麻木、同變得冷漠。"},{"pid":"be62916da7ea313478e8a3b311a3bcd7a986f338","tid":2064052,"uid":134546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T13:47:40.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"20a6335bf10e4bb1dc5bb0caca9b0672fd9c659a","tid":2064052,"uid":257847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be62916da7ea313478e8a3b311a3bcd7a986f338","tid":2064052,"uid":134546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T13:47:40.000Z","msg":"加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T13:49:02.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb7a4fd564f597a5a11587947efee1564ffaf8d","tid":2064052,"uid":257847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T13:53:33.000Z","msg":"冇力照推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb1868449c1f52d657533956c51e0c929b92a0a","tid":2064052,"uid":257847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T14:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f2379f9b1f6284f370d0b87b4c8740053f30acd","tid":2064052,"uid":257847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T14:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f625d1f475f5dbc2b91db62f10f60b2c9dca9fce","tid":2064052,"uid":257847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T14:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94487057c665bf6d864bf7246bfe41eefafab3e","tid":2064052,"uid":257847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T14:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反應冷淡"},{"pid":"907fb0bb07981d315490497ef89b7cb382fd21bc","tid":2064052,"uid":257847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T15:12:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7249573efc9f1619f0c416262369fefe412785e","tid":2064052,"uid":257847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T16:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望聽朝多啲人睇到"},{"pid":"3c324bdc29a0c502df3f18c517929cf01bfb91ff","tid":2064052,"uid":144718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T16:59:53.000Z","msg":"曾赤手抵擋困境 <br />\n<br />\n好有畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0009e76ee5189952094301897f5a4fb6c1dfc4","tid":2064052,"uid":279321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T17:03:27.000Z","msg":"P牌冇得正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/cat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62484f3895f6aa05d3fdbe89577029a25358cd4","tid":2064052,"uid":257847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c324bdc29a0c502df3f18